statements: SELECT * FROM proteomics_data;
SELECT protein_id, peptide_sequence, spectral_count FROM proteomics_data;
SELECT experiment_id, source_database, peptide_evidence FROM proteomics_data ORDER BY experiment_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM proteomics_data WHERE spectral_count > 100;
SELECT protein_id, peptide_sequence, spectral_count FROM proteomics_data WHERE source_database = 'SwissProt';
SELECT * FROM proteomics_data WHERE spectral_count > 100
SELECT DISTINCT source_database, COUNT(DISTINCT protein_id) AS protein_count FROM proteomics_data GROUP BY source_database
SELECT experiment_id, protein_id, peptide_sequence FROM proteomics_data WHERE source_database = 'SwissProt' ORDER BY protein_id DESC
SELECT experiment_id, protein_id, COUNT(peptide_sequence) AS peptide_count FROM proteomics_data GROUP BY experiment_id, protein_id
SELECT * FROM proteomics_data WHERE peptide_evidence LIKE '%validated%'
SELECT protein_id, protein_name, protein_sequence FROM Proteins;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, researcher_name, experiment_date FROM Experiments;
SELECT * FROM Proteins WHERE created_at > '2022-01-01';
SELECT experiment_name, researcher_name FROM Experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT protein_name, protein_sequence FROM Proteins WHERE source_id = '9b15e68e-1602-4e5b-a7d1-0990cb1b7173';
SELECT * FROM Proteins WHERE protein_id = '12345678-1234-5678-1234-567812345678'
SELECT protein_id, protein_name FROM Proteins WHERE protein_name LIKE '%ABC%' ORDER BY created_at DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Proteins WHERE updated_at > '2022-01-01 00:00:00'
SELECT experiment_name, researcher_name, experiment_date FROM Experiments WHERE source_id = '87654321-4321-8765-4321-876543218765' ORDER BY experiment_date ASC
SELECT * FROM Proteins p JOIN Experiments e ON p.source_id = e.source_id WHERE p.created_at < '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND e.created_at > '2021-01-01 00:00:00'
SELECT * FROM proteomics_data_source;
SELECT source_name, created_date FROM proteomics_data_source ORDER BY created_date DESC;
SELECT protein_name, protein_mass FROM protein_data WHERE protein_mass > 1000;
SELECT * FROM experimental_data WHERE experiment_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT experiment_type, result FROM experimental_data ORDER BY result ASC;
SELECT * FROM proteomics_data_source;
SELECT protein_name, protein_mass, source_name FROM protein_data JOIN proteomics_data_source ON protein_data.source_id = proteomics_data_source.source_id;
SELECT experiment_type, experiment_date, result FROM experimental_data WHERE result LIKE '%positive%' ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;

SELECT source_name, COUNT(protein_id) AS num_proteins FROM proteomics_data_source JOIN protein_data ON proteomics_data_source.source_id = protein_data.source_id GROUP BY source_name ORDER BY num_proteins DESC;
SELECT * FROM protein_data WHERE protein_mass > 50 ORDER BY protein_mass ASC;
SELECT * FROM Proteins;
SELECT id, protein_name FROM Proteins ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT protein_name, molecular_weight FROM Proteins WHERE molecular_weight > 100;
SELECT * FROM Peptides JOIN Proteins ON Peptides.protein_id = Proteins.id;
SELECT experiment_name, description FROM Experiments WHERE date_performed >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Proteins ORDER BY protein_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, protein_name, molecular_weight FROM Proteins WHERE molecular_weight > 50 ORDER BY molecular_weight DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT Peptides.id, Peptides.peptide_sequence, Proteins.protein_name FROM Peptides INNER JOIN Proteins ON Peptides.protein_id = Proteins.id ORDER BY Peptides.id ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT Spectra.spectrum_data, Proteins.protein_name FROM Spectra INNER JOIN Peptides ON Spectra.peptide_id = Peptides.id INNER JOIN Proteins ON Peptides.protein_id = Proteins.id ORDER BY Spectra.id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM Experiments WHERE date_performed BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM Proteins;
SELECT protein_name, molecular_weight FROM Proteins WHERE molecular_weight > 100;
SELECT * FROM Peptides WHERE start_position = 1;
SELECT peptide_sequence, start_position, end_position FROM Peptides WHERE end_position - start_position > 5;
SELECT DISTINCT researcher_id, full_name FROM Researchers;
SELECT * FROM Proteins WHERE molecular_weight > 1000 ORDER BY protein_id DESC
SELECT protein_name, sequence FROM Proteins JOIN Peptides ON Proteins.protein_id = Peptides.protein_id WHERE Peptides.end_position - Peptides.start_position > 10
SELECT protein_name, molecular_weight FROM Proteins JOIN PeptideIdentification ON Proteins.protein_id = PeptideIdentification.peptide_id WHERE PeptideIdentification.confidence_level > 0.8
SELECT DISTINCT experiment_name, researcher_id FROM Experiments JOIN PeptideIdentification ON Experiments.experiment_id = PeptideIdentification.experiment_id ORDER BY researcher_id ASC
SELECT full_name, email FROM Researchers WHERE affiliation LIKE '%University%' ORDER BY full_name
